snippet.title: Seawolf/Missile for the Bally Astrocade
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

Seawolf/Missile is a 2-games pack, for 1 or 2 players.

In Seawolf the player(s) take command over a submarine, in Missile over an Anti-Air turret.


What I think:

2 okay games in 1...
